        <!-- トッピクス -->\r\n          <section class=\"topTopicSec\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n            <div class=\"topTopicSec__wrap\"> \r\n              <div class=\"topTopicSec__inner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n                <div class=\"topTopicSec__titleBox\">\r\n                  <div class=\"c-decorativeTitle-blue topTopicSec__decorativeTitle\">TOPICS </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"c-heading-blue topTopicSec__heading\">トピックス</div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"topTopicSec__descBox\">\r\n                  <p class=\"topTopicSec__desc\">当社のアクアソリューション分野（バイオマス利活用施設、汚泥再生処理に関する事業）は、会社分割により、2023年10月1日に月島JFEアクアソリューショングループに移管されました。</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"topTopicSec__desc\">施設の設計・調達・建設・修繕に関する事業 →<br class=\"u-spDb\"><a class=\"u-link\" href=\"https://www.tsk-g.co.jp/tech/water-environmental/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">月島JFEアクアソリューション（株）</a></p>\r\n                  <p class=\"topTopicSec__desc\">施設の運転管理に関する事業 →<br class=\"u-spDb\"><a class=\"u-link\" href=\"https://www.t-tms.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">月島ジェイテクノメンテサービス（株）</a></p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"topTopicSec__listBox\">\r\n                  <ul class=\"c-topic__list\">\r\n\t\t    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/260330.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2026.03.30</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">神奈川県足柄上衛生組合より一般廃棄物処理施設の整備運営事業を受注</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/251223.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2025.12.23</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">大分県日田市より一般廃棄物処理施設の整備運営事業を受注</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/251127.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2025.11.27</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">廃棄物焼却施設の基幹的設備改良工事における不適切な保護具使用について<br class=\"u-pcDb\">（追加調査の結果）</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/251021.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2025.10.21</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">海浜幕張駅階段に共同広告を掲出いたしました。</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/251014.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2025.10.14</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">廃棄物焼却施設の基幹的設備改良工事における不適切な保護具使用について</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/240507.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2024.05.07</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">御坊広域行政事務組合/ごみ処理施設基幹的設備改良工事の竣工について</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/240426.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2024.04.26</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">甲賀広域行政組合/ごみ処理施設基幹的設備改良工事の竣工について</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/231127.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2023.11.27</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">浜松市より「第二期浜松市西部清掃工場 運営・維持管理等業務」を受注しました。</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/231001.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2023.10.01</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">当社アクア事業分割移管のお知らせ。</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/231001-1.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2023.10.01</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">ホームページをリニューアルしました。</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/230706.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2023.07.06</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">『下水道展‘23札幌』に出展いたします。</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/230411.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2023.04.11</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">君津市衛生センター整備工事が竣工しました。</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                    <li class=\"c-topic__listItem-top\"><a class=\"c-topic__listItemLink\" href=\"./topics/230401.html\">\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-left\"> \r\n                          <time class=\"c-topic__date\">2023.04.01</time>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"c-topic__listItem-right\">\r\n                          <p class=\"c-topic__titleText\">ホームページを全面リニューアルしました。</p>\r\n                        </div></a></li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"topTopicSec__toListPageBox\"><a class=\"topTopicSec__toListPageLink\" href=\"./topics/\"> <img class=\"topTopicSec__toListPageIcon\" src=\"./_assets/images/common/icon_cube.png\" alt=\"トピックス一覧\"><span class=\"topTopicSec__toListPageText\">トピックス一覧</span><img class=\"topTopicSec__toListPageArrow-gray\" src=\"./_assets/images/common/icon_arrow-filled-gray.png\" alt=\"トピックス一覧\"><img class=\"topTopicSec__toListPageArrow-blue\" src=\"./_assets/images/common/icon_arrow-filled-blue.png\" alt=\"トピックス一覧\"></a></div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </section>\r\n          <sectin class=\"topBusinessSec\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n            <div class=\"topBusinessSec__wrap\">\r\n              <div class=\"topBusinessSec__inner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n                <div class=\"topBusinessSec__content\">\r\n                  <div class=\"topBusinessSec__content-left\"> \r\n                    <div class=\"topBusinessSec__titleBox\">\r\n                      <div class=\"c-decorativeTitle-white topBusinessSec__decorativeTitle\">BUSINESS </div>\r\n                      <div class=\"c-heading-blue topBusinessSec__heading\">事業紹介</div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topBusinessSec__headingMiddleBox\">\r\n                      <div class=\"c-headingMiddle-blue\">廃棄物の処理・利活用で<br>くらしを支え、環境をまもる<br>人と技術を融合させ、<br>最適なソリューションを提供</div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topBusinessSec__textBox\">\r\n                      <p class=\"topBusinessSec__text\">JETが誇るのは資源の環境とエネルギーの利活用技術。<br class=\"u-pcDb\"></p>\r\n                      <p class=\"topBusinessSec__text\">それらを下支えするのが、豊富な実績に基づくEPCと<br class=\"u-pcDb\">安全・安心・安定なO＆Mです。</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topBusinessSec__smallTxtBox\"> \r\n                      <p class=\"topBusinessSec__smallTxt\">EPC：設計=Engineering、資材調達=Procurement、建設=Construction</p>\r\n                      <p class=\"topBusinessSec__smallTxt\">O&M：運転=Operation、維持管理=Maintenance</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topBusinessSec__btnBox\"><a class=\"c-btn-blue topBusinessSec__btnLink\" href=\"./business/\">詳しく見る</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"topBusinessSec__content-right\"> \r\n                    <figure class=\"topBusinessSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topBusinessSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_businessImg03.png\" alt=\"EPC × O&amp;M\"></figure>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </sectin>\r\n          <sectin class=\"topCorporateSec\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n            <div class=\"topCorporateSec__wrap\"> \r\n              <div class=\"topCorporateSec__inner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n                <div class=\"topCorporateSec__content\">\r\n                  <div class=\"topCorporateSec__content-left\"> \r\n                    <div class=\"topCorporateSec__titleBox\">\r\n                      <div class=\"c-decorativeTitle-green topCorporateSec__decorativeTitle\">CORPORATE</div>\r\n                      <div class=\"c-heading-blue topCorporateSec__heading\">会社情報</div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <figure class=\"topCorporateSec__contentImgBox-sp\"><img class=\"topCorporateSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_corporateImg01.jpg\" alt=\"会社情報\"></figure>\r\n                    <div class=\"topCorporateSec__headingMiddleBox\">\r\n                      <div class=\"c-headingMiddle-blue\">社会の、地域の持続可能性を<br>根底で支える<br>環境分野のエキスパート</div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topCorporateSec__textBox\">\r\n                      <p class=\"topCorporateSec__text\">40年近くにわたりサステナビリティをリードし、<br class=\"u-pcDb\">支えて続けてきた当社の全体像を俯瞰</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topCorporateSec__btnBox\"><a class=\"c-btn-blue topCorporateSec__btnLink\" href=\"./company/\">詳しく見る</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"topCorporateSec__content-right\"> \r\n                    <figure class=\"topCorporateSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topCorporateSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_corporateImg01.jpg\" alt=\"会社情報\"></figure>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </sectin>\r\n          <sectin class=\"topRecruitSec\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n            <div class=\"topRecruitSec__wrap\">\r\n              <div class=\"topRecruitSec__inner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                <div class=\"topRecruitSec__content\">\r\n                  <div class=\"topRecruitSec__content-left\"> \r\n                    <div class=\"topRecruitSec__titleBox\">\r\n                      <div class=\"c-decorativeTitle-whiteTranparent topRecruitSec__decorativeTitle\">RECRUIT</div>\r\n                      <div class=\"c-heading-blue topRecruitSec__heading\">採用情報</div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImg-sp\">\r\n                      <figure class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_recruitImg01.jpg\" alt=\"採用情報\"></figure>\r\n                      <figure class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_recruitImg02.jpg\" alt=\"採用情報\"></figure>\r\n                      <figure class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_recruitImg03.jpg\" alt=\"採用情報\"></figure>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topRecruitSec__headingMiddleBox\">\r\n                      <div class=\"c-headingMiddle-blue\">共に果敢にトライする<br>気概を持った仲間を<br>求めています。</div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topRecruitSec__textBox\">\r\n                      <p class=\"topRecruitSec__text\">私たちは、当社の前身となった企<br class=\"u-pcDb\">業から受け継いだ「挑戦する<br class=\"u-pcDb\">DNA」を呼び覚まし、共に挑戦す<br class=\"u-pcDb\">る仲間を求めています。</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"topRecruitSec__btnBox\"><a class=\"c-btn-blue topRecruitSec__btnLink\" href=\"./recruit/\">詳しく見る</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"topRecruitSec__content-right\"> \r\n                    <figure class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_recruitImg01.jpg\" alt=\"採用情報\"></figure>\r\n                    <figure class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_recruitImg02.jpg\" alt=\"採用情報\"></figure>\r\n                    <figure class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImgBox\"><img class=\"topRecruitSec__contentImg\" src=\"./_assets/images/top/top_recruitImg03.jpg\" alt=\"採用情報\"></figure>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </sectin>\r\n          <sectin class=\"topContactSec\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n            <div class=\"topContactSec__wrap\"> \r\n              <div class=\"topContactSec__inner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">  \r\n                <div class=\"topContactSec__contactBox\">\r\n                  <div class=\"c-contactArea\"> <a class=\"c-contactArea__link\" href=\"./inquiry/\">\r\n                      <div class=\"c-contactArea__link-left\">  <span class=\"c-contactArea__text\">お問い合わせ</span></div>\r\n                      <div class=\"c-contactArea__link-right\">  \r\n                        <div class=\"c-decorativeSmallTitle-whiteTranparent c-contactArea__heading\">CONTACT</div>\r\n                      </div></a></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </sectin>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </main>\r\n    <footer class=\"siteFooter\">\r\n      <div class=\"siteFo